{"updated":1769694847,"is_labeled":false,"copyright_permission":"need_review","settings":{"table_of_contents":{"enabled":false}},"excerpt":"如何将Google Highway（跨架构SIMD抽象库）与MLIR/LLVM（编译器基础设施）结合，核心目标是搭建一套面向AI芯片的SIMD向量化算子编译流程——既利用Highway简化跨架构SIMD代码编写，又借助MLIR/LLVM完成从高层抽象到AI芯片原生指令的编译优化与代码生成。以下是 分层架构、实操步骤、核心代码示例和关键优化要点，全程围绕AI芯片算子开发场景展开。一、核心结合逻辑与分层架构Google Highway和MLIR/LLVM的结合是“分工协作”模式： …","admin_closed_comment":false,"voting":0,"article_type":"normal","reason":"","force_login_when_click_read_more":false,"excerpt_title":"","id":"1988018964505321845","voteup_count":3,"title_image":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-decb95e5b11e4fad25e94ffd74c8a0e2_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b","has_column":true,"url":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1988018964505321845","comment_permission":"censor","author":{"is_followed":false,"avatar_url_template":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-eb249fe9f1461ad37894b3362aa80eb4.jpg?source=d16d100b","uid":"1019697603679793152","user_type":"people","is_following":false,"type":"people","url_token":"changping123","id":"8ffff72080e204609981e6e00fe98684","description":"某Ai芯片公司架构师","name":"常平","is_advertiser":false,"headline":"为学，闻道，践行！","gender":1,"url":"/people/8ffff72080e204609981e6e00fe98684","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-eb249fe9f1461ad37894b3362aa80eb4_l.jpg?source=d16d100b","is_org":false,"badge":[]},"comment_count":0,"created":1766761403,"content":"<p data-pid=\"ZXxAEpRS\">如何将Google Highway（跨架构SIMD抽象库）与MLIR/LLVM（编译器基础设施）结合，核心目标是搭建一套面向AI芯片的SIMD向量化算子编译流程——既利用Highway简化跨架构SIMD代码编写，又借助MLIR/LLVM完成从高层抽象到AI芯片原生指令的编译优化与代码生成。以下是<b>分层架构、实操步骤、核心代码示例</b>和关键优化要点，全程围绕AI芯片算子开发场景展开。</p><h3>一、核心结合逻辑与分层架构</h3><p data-pid=\"hn-9CmY2\">Google Highway和MLIR/LLVM的结合是“分工协作”模式：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"1NH1o30K\"><b>Highway</b>：作为<b>前端编程层</b>，屏蔽不同架构SIMD指令差异，让你用统一接口编写AI算子的向量化逻辑（无需关心底层指令）；</li><li data-pid=\"Sf_wHemP\"><b>MLIR</b>：作为<b>中间优化层</b>，将Highway的SIMD抽象转换为MLIR的向量/张量IR，完成AI算子级优化（如循环分块、指令融合、内存布局调整）；</li><li data-pid=\"H-uUFYAU\"><b>LLVM</b>：作为<b>后端代码生成层</b>，将MLIR优化后的IR转换为LLVM IR，最终生成目标AI芯片的原生SIMD指令。</li></ul><p data-pid=\"-72mtamw\">整体架构如下（面向AI芯片算子场景）：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-7fc9f33cc19f334f78f015a62ccfc0c2_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"313\" data-rawheight=\"702\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"313\"></figure><h3>二、具体结合步骤（实操版）</h3><p data-pid=\"VTkHquEH\">以下步骤基于“AI芯片GEMM算子向量化”场景展开，从代码编写到指令生成完整落地：</p><h3>步骤1：基于Highway编写SIMD化的AI算子（前端）</h3><p data-pid=\"tMLaoN3s\">首先用Highway的统一接口编写AI算子的向量化逻辑，聚焦“算法逻辑”而非“底层指令”。以FP32 GEMM算子的向量乘加为例：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span></span><span class=\"c1\">// 1. 引入Highway头文件</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span> <span class=\"cpf\">\"highway/highway.h\"</span><span class=\"cp\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">namespace</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">highway</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">// 2. 定义适配AI芯片的向量类型（256bit=8个FP32）</span>\n<span class=\"k\">constexpr</span> <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">VEC_WIDTH</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"c1\">// 目标AI芯片的向量寄存器宽度（256bit）</span>\n<span class=\"k\">using</span> <span class=\"n\">VecF32</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Vec</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">float</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Fixed</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">VEC_WIDTH</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">// 3. Highway实现的SIMD化GEMM核心逻辑（向量化乘加）</span>\n<span class=\"kt\">void</span> <span class=\"nf\">GEMMHighway</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">float</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">float</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kt\">float</span><span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> \n                 <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">N</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 分块遍历（适配AI芯片缓存）</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">m</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">m</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"o\">++</span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">N</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">+=</span> <span class=\"n\">VEC_WIDTH</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">VecF32</span> <span class=\"n\">sum</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Zero</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">VecF32</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">();</span> <span class=\"c1\">// 向量累加器</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">k</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">k</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"o\">++</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"c1\">// 1. 加载B的向量（SIMD访存）</span>\n        <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">VecF32</span> <span class=\"n\">b_vec</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">LoadUnaligned</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">VecF32</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">N</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"p\">]);</span>\n        <span class=\"c1\">// 2. 广播A的标量到向量 + 向量乘加（核心SIMD运算）</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">sum</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">MulAdd</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"p\">(</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">K</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"p\">]</span> <span class=\"p\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">b_vec</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">sum</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n      <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"c1\">// 3. 存储结果到C（SIMD访存）</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">StoreUnaligned</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">sum</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">N</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"p\">]);</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"34MHERHl\">这一步的核心是：<b>用Highway屏蔽AI芯片SIMD指令的细节，只关注算子的向量化逻辑</b>。</p><h3>步骤2：将Highway代码接入MLIR（中间层桥接）</h3><p data-pid=\"38GOyQs1\">MLIR的核心价值是“模块化优化”，需将Highway的SIMD逻辑转换为MLIR的<code>VectorDialect</code>（向量IR）或<code>LinalgDialect</code>（张量IR），有两种主流方式：</p><h3>方式1：MLIR封装Highway接口（轻量集成，适合快速验证）</h3><p data-pid=\"4qAeNhma\">直接在MLIR的C++ Pass中调用Highway编写的算子函数，将Highway作为“预编译的SIMD函数库”，MLIR负责高层算子的调度优化（如分块、并行化）：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span></span><span class=\"c1\">// MLIR Pass中调用Highway算子（伪代码）</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span> <span class=\"cpf\">\"mlir/Dialect/Linalg/IR/Linalg.h\"</span><span class=\"cp\"></span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span> <span class=\"cpf\">\"mlir/Pass/Pass.h\"</span><span class=\"cp\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">// 定义MLIR Pass：将Linalg GEMM映射到Highway实现</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nl\">LinalgGEMMToHighwayPass</span> \n    <span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"k\">public</span> <span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PassWrapper</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">LinalgGEMMToHighwayPass</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">OperationPass</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ModuleOp</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"kt\">void</span> <span class=\"n\">runOnOperation</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"k\">override</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">auto</span> <span class=\"n\">module</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">getOperation</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n    <span class=\"c1\">// 遍历模块中的Linalg GEMM算子</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">walk</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"p\">](</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">linalg</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">GenericOp</span> <span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"n\">isGEMMOp</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">))</span> <span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n      \n      <span class=\"c1\">// 1. 提取GEMM的维度、内存布局等参数</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">auto</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">getDimSize</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">auto</span> <span class=\"n\">N</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">getDimSize</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">auto</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">getDimSize</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n      \n      <span class=\"c1\">// 2. 调用Highway实现的GEMM函数（桥接核心）</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">OpBuilder</span> <span class=\"n\">builder</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">auto</span> <span class=\"n\">highwayCall</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">builder</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">func</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">CallOp</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getLoc</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n          <span class=\"s\">\"GEMMHighway\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"c1\">// 对应步骤1的Highway函数名</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getResultTypes</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n          <span class=\"c1\">// 传递参数：A/B/C指针 + 维度</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ValueRange</span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getInputs</span><span class=\"p\">()[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getInputs</span><span class=\"p\">()[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> \n                           <span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getOutputs</span><span class=\"p\">()[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">N</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"p\">);</span>\n      \n      <span class=\"c1\">// 3. 替换原Linalg GEMM算子为Highway调用</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">replaceAllUsesWith</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">highwayCall</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getResults</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">genericOp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">erase</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">});</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">};</span>\n</code></pre></div><h3>方式2：自定义Highway→MLIR转换（深度集成，适合量产）</h3><p data-pid=\"SA60ok7D\">若需对Highway的SIMD逻辑做精细化优化，需将Highway的内部IR（或抽象语法树）转换为MLIR的<code>VectorDialect</code>，核心步骤：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"d6o9nvnO\">解析Highway的向量操作（如<code>hwy::Add</code>/<code>hwy::MulAdd</code>），映射为MLIR <code>vector.add</code>/<code>vector.mul_add</code>；</li><li data-pid=\"QTlM0RRP\">将Highway的向量类型（如<code>VecF32</code>）映射为MLIR <code>vector&lt;8xf32&gt;</code>（对应256bit向量）；</li><li data-pid=\"JbAqzfnZ\">实现自定义MLIR转换Pass，完成上述映射。</li></ol><p data-pid=\"XtJ7JS5O\">示例代码（Highway操作→MLIR VectorOp）：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span></span><span class=\"c1\">// 自定义Highway到MLIR VectorOp的映射函数</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Value</span> <span class=\"n\">mapHighwayOpToMLIR</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">OpBuilder</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">builder</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> \n                               <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Operation</span> <span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"c1\">// Highway操作</span>\n                               <span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ValueRange</span> <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">switch</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">kind</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">case</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">OpKind</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"nl\">Add</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"c1\">// Highway Add → MLIR vector.add</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">builder</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">vector</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">AddOp</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">builder</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getUnknownLoc</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span> <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">].</span><span class=\"n\">getType</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span> <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">]);</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">case</span> <span class=\"n\">hwy</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">OpKind</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"nl\">MulAdd</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"c1\">// Highway MulAdd → MLIR vector.mul_add</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">builder</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">vector</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">FMulAddOp</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">builder</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getUnknownLoc</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span> <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">].</span><span class=\"n\">getType</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span> \n          <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">operands</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">]);</span>\n    <span class=\"c1\">// 其他操作（Load/Store/Broadcast）同理映射</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">default</span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">llvm_unreachable</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"Unsupported Highway operation!\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div><h3>步骤3：MLIR层面的AI算子优化（核心价值）</h3><p data-pid=\"HhKdquJY\">将Highway逻辑转换为MLIR后，利用MLIR的模块化Dialect完成<b>AI芯片定制化优化</b>（这是MLIR的核心优势）：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span></span><span class=\"c1\">// MLIR优化Pass链（面向AI芯片）</span>\n<span class=\"kt\">void</span> <span class=\"nf\">buildAIChipOptimizationPipeline</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">OpPassManager</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 1. 向量级优化：调整向量长度适配AI芯片（如256bit→512bit）</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">addPass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">createVectorTransformsPass</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 2. 内存优化：向量化访存对齐（适配AI芯片64字节对齐要求）</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">addPass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">createVectorMemoryOptPass</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 3. 张量级优化：GEMM分块（适配AI芯片缓存大小）</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">addPass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">createLinalgTilePass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">TileSizesOption</span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"mi\">32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">32</span><span class=\"p\">}));</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 4. 指令融合：将mul+add融合为AI芯片的FMA指令</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">addPass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">createVectorFusionPass</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div><h3>步骤4：MLIR→LLVM IR转换（对接后端）</h3><p data-pid=\"ZGblhp6R\">MLIR提供原生的<code>ConvertVectorToLLVM</code> Pass，可将优化后的<code>VectorDialect</code>直接转换为LLVM IR，无需手动编码：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span></span><span class=\"c1\">// MLIR→LLVM IR转换</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ModuleOp</span> <span class=\"n\">convertMLIRToLLVMIR</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ModuleOp</span> <span class=\"n\">mlirModule</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">PassManager</span> <span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlirModule</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getContext</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 启用MLIR→LLVM IR转换Pass</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">addPass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">createConvertVectorToLLVMPass</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">addPass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">createConvertFuncToLLVMPass</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 运行Pass并返回LLVM IR模块</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlir</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">failed</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">pm</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mlirModule</span><span class=\"p\">)))</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">errs</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"s\">\"MLIR to LLVM IR conversion failed!</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"k\">nullptr</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">mlirModule</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div><h3>步骤5：LLVM对接AI芯片后端（生成原生SIMD指令）</h3><p data-pid=\"cwLCVw_h\">LLVM负责将LLVM IR转换为目标AI芯片的原生SIMD指令，核心是<b>扩展LLVM的Target后端</b>，适配AI芯片的SIMD指令集：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"qLnvCmVo\">为目标AI芯片新增LLVM Target（如<code>MyAIChipTarget</code>），定义向量寄存器、指令集（如<code>VADD.F32</code>/<code>VMUL.F32</code>）；</li><li data-pid=\"P7Ud6lgB\">实现LLVM <code>TargetLowering</code>类，将LLVM IR的向量操作（如<code>llvm::VectorType</code>的add/mul）映射为AI芯片的原生SIMD指令；</li><li data-pid=\"WiJOBymj\">编译生成目标代码（汇编/机器码）。</li></ol><p data-pid=\"EEHC_t4d\">示例：LLVM TargetLowering中映射向量乘加指令：</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span></span><span class=\"c1\">// 自定义AI芯片的TargetLowering</span>\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">MyAIChipTargetLowering</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"k\">public</span> <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">TargetLowering</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"k\">public</span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">MyAIChipTargetLowering</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">LLVMContext</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">ctx</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"n\">MyAIChipTargetMachine</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">tm</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">TargetLowering</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tm</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"c1\">// 映射LLVM IR的fmuladd到AI芯片的VFMA指令</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">setOperationAction</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ISD</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">FMULADD</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">MVT</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">v8f32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> \n                       <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">TargetLowering</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Custom</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c1\">// 自定义指令选择：将FMULADD转换为AI芯片的VFMA指令</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">SDValue</span> <span class=\"n\">LowerOperation</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">SDValue</span> <span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">SelectionDAG</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">dag</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"k\">const</span> <span class=\"k\">override</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getOpcode</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ISD</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">FMULADD</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"c1\">// 构造AI芯片的VFMA指令（256bit FP32向量乘加）</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">dag</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getMachineNode</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">MyAIChip</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">VFMA</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getLoc</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span> \n                                <span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getValueType</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span> <span class=\"n\">op</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">getOperands</span><span class=\"p\">());</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">SDValue</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">};</span>\n</code></pre></div><h3>步骤6：验证与性能调优</h3><ol><li data-pid=\"awXQv0hk\"><b>功能验证</b>：对比Highway原生代码和MLIR/LLVM编译后的代码输出，确保结果一致；</li><li data-pid=\"yAneXKTM\"><b>性能调优</b>：</li></ol><ul><li data-pid=\"q70Hbq3u\">调整MLIR的分块大小（适配AI芯片缓存）；</li><li data-pid=\"F_ZbWLZV\">优化LLVM的寄存器分配（减少向量寄存器溢出）；</li><li data-pid=\"28ABzie7\">调整Highway的向量粒度（如VEC_WIDTH）匹配AI芯片的SIMD单元。</li></ul><h3>三、关键集成要点（避坑指南）</h3><h3>1. Highway与MLIR VectorDialect的映射规则</h3><table data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"table\" data-size=\"normal\" data-row-style=\"normal\"><tbody><tr><th>Highway概念</th><th>MLIR VectorDialect对应概念</th><th>示例映射</th></tr><tr><td>Vec&lt;float, 8&gt;</td><td>vector&lt;8xf32&gt;</td><td>256bit FP32向量</td></tr><tr><td>hwy::Add(a, b)</td><td>vector.add %a, %b : vector&lt;8xf32&gt;</td><td>向量加法</td></tr><tr><td>hwy::Load&lt;VecF32&gt;</td><td>vector.load %ptr : vector&lt;8xf32&gt;</td><td>向量访存</td></tr><tr><td>hwy::Broadcast(x)</td><td>vector.broadcast %x : f32 to vector&lt;8xf32&gt;</td><td>标量广播到向量</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>2. 性能平衡：Highway抽象 vs MLIR优化</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"eTVGmte0\">Highway的抽象会引入少量开销，需通过MLIR的“指令融合”“常量折叠”Pass消除；</li><li data-pid=\"m6QfdeJu\">避免过度封装：核心SIMD操作直接映射到MLIR，而非通过Highway间接调用。</li></ul><h3>3. 跨架构适配</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"mkStp_DK\">利用MLIR的<code>TargetAttr</code>区分不同AI芯片架构（如A100/自研芯片）；</li><li data-pid=\"qckdbL8U\">为不同架构定制Highway的向量宽度（如128bit，256bit）。</li></ul><h3>四、总结</h3><ol><li data-pid=\"Gg-8tCz9\"><b>核心分工</b>：Highway负责“统一SIMD编程接口”，MLIR负责“AI算子级优化”，LLVM负责“底层指令生成”；</li><li data-pid=\"g-vPb3bR\"><b>集成路径</b>：优先用“MLIR封装Highway接口”快速验证，再用“Highway→MLIR转换”做深度优化；</li><li data-pid=\"kTh_NB3U\"><b>关键优化</b>：MLIR侧聚焦张量分块/指令融合，LLVM侧聚焦SIMD指令映射/寄存器分配，两者结合才能发挥AI芯片的性能上限。</li></ol><p data-pid=\"E0vtlStG\">这套组合的核心价值是：既降低了跨架构SIMD算子的开发成本（Highway），又保留了对AI芯片的定制化优化能力（MLIR/LLVM），是AI芯片编译器中SIMD向量化编程模型的最优实践之一。</p>","state":"published","content_need_truncated":true,"image_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-decb95e5b11e4fad25e94ffd74c8a0e2_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b","title":"第110篇 - Google Highway 与 MLIR/LLVM 融合：打造 AI 芯片 SIMD 向量化流程","can_comment":{"status":true,"reason":"请输入评论，您的评论将会由作者筛选后显示"},"type":"article","suggest_edit":{"status":false,"url":"","reason":"","tip":"","title":""}}
